Token.Abstract: NSData+GlucoseMeasurementParser provides glucose measurement response parsing
Returns a dictionary with all the data of the glucose measurement characteristic. Keys and enumerations are defined in the UHNBGMConstants.h file, which is imported with this category.

Parameter.Name: crcPresent
Parameter.Abstract: Indicates whether the characteristic includes the E2E-CRC field

ReturnValue.Abstract: All the data of the glucose measurement characteristic as a NSDictionary
